preibisch_imagej

Class ChannelCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • preibisch_imagej.ChannelCollection

  • public class ChannelCollection
extends Object
    A ChannelCollection maintains a list of data values. The data is read only. One can request any channel number from a ChannelCollection. If there is no data associated with a channel number the value returned is zero.
    Author:
    Barry DeZonia
